About: Something's rotten in the land of the dead, and
you're being played for a sucker. Meet Manny Calavera,
travel agent at the Department of Death. He sells luxury
packages to souls on their four-year journey to eternal
rest. But there's trouble in paradise. Help Manny untangle
himself from a conspiracy that threatens his very salvation.

One of the most acclaimed adventure games of all time is now
back, better than ever. Grim Fandango's epic story of four
years in the life (or death) of Manny Calavera, travel agent
to the dead, has been remastered to look, sound, and control
even better than when it won GameSpot's Game of the Year award
upon its original launch. Grim Fandango still stands as a
classic of the genre, with unforgettable characters and unique
combination of film noir and Mexican folklore.

Grim Fandango Remastered includes:

* Repainted, hi-res character textures
* New, dynamic lighting
* Classic score re-recorded with a full live orchestra
* Over 2 hours of exclusive developer commentary
* Concept art browser
